{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solve\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">solve</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">scope</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Scope\">Scope</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">goal</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGenM\">VCGenM</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The main VC generation step. Operates on a plain `MVarId` with no knowledge of grind.\nReturns `.goals subgoals` when the goal was decomposed, or a classification result\n(`.noEntailment`, `.noProgramFoundInTarget`, etc.) when no further decomposition is possible.\n\nThe function performs the following steps in order:\n\n1. **Forall introduction**: If the target is a `∀`, introduce binders via `Sym.intros`.\n2. **Triple unfolding**: If the target is `⦃P⦄ x ⦃Q⦄`, unfold into `P ⊢ₛ wp⟦x⟧ Q`.\n3. **PostCond.entails decomposition**: Split `PostCond.entails` into its components.\n4. **Lambda introduction**: If the RHS `T` in `H ⊢ₛ T` is a lambda, introduce an extra state\n   variable via `SPred.entails_cons_intro`.\n5. **Proj/beta reduction**: Reduce `Prod.fst`/`Prod.snd` projections and beta redexes in\n   both `H` and `T` (e.g., `(fun _ => T, Q.snd).fst s` → `T`).\n6. **Syntactic rfl**: If `T` is not a `PredTrans.apply`, try closing by `SPred.entails.refl`.\n7. **Let-hoisting**: Hoist let-expressions from the program head to the goal target.\n7a. **Let-zeta/intro**: If the target starts with `let`, zeta immediately if duplicable, else\n    introduce into the local context via `introsSimp`.\n7b. **Fvar zeta**: Unfold local let-bound fvars on demand when they appear as the program head.\n8. **Iota reduction**: Reduce matchers/recursors with concrete discriminants.\n9. **ite/dite/match splitting**: Apply the appropriate split backward rule.\n10. **Spec application**: Look up a registered `@[spec]` theorem (triple or simp) and apply\n    its cached backward rule.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solve","kind":"def","line":188,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.solve","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L188-L286"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.stop\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">stop</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Stop decomposing and emit the current goal as a VC (out of fuel, or `until` matched). ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.stop","kind":"ctor","line":44,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.stop","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L44-L45"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.goals\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">goals</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">scope</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Context.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Scope\">Scope</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">subgoals</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Successfully decomposed the goal. These are the subgoals, sharing `scope`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.goals","kind":"ctor","line":42,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.goals","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L42-L43"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noSpecFoundForProgram\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">noSpecFoundForProgram</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e </span><span class=\"fn\">monad</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">thms</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/SpecDB.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.SpecAttr.SpecTheoremNew\">SpecAttr.SpecTheoremNew</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Did not find a spec for the `e` in `H ⊢ₛ wp⟦e⟧ Q s₁ ... sₙ`.\nCandidates were `thms`, but none of them matched the monad.\n","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noSpecFoundForProgram","kind":"ctor","line":37,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noSpecFoundForProgram","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L37-L41"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noStrategyForProgram\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">noStrategyForProgram</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">e</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Don't know how to handle `e` in `H ⊢ₛ wp⟦e⟧ Q s₁ ... sₙ`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noStrategyForProgram","kind":"ctor","line":35,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noStrategyForProgram","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L35-L36"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noProgramFoundInTarget\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">noProgramFoundInTarget</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">T</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The `T` in `H ⊢ₛ T` was not of the form `wp⟦e⟧ Q s₁ ... sₙ`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noProgramFoundInTarget","kind":"ctor","line":33,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noProgramFoundInTarget","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L33-L34"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noEntailment\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span>.<span class=\"name\">noEntailment</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">target</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.Expr\">Expr</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\">SolveResult</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`target` was not of the form `H ⊢ₛ T`. ","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noEntailment","kind":"ctor","line":31,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult.noEntailment","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L31-L32"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">Elab</span>.<span class=\"name\">Tactic</span>.<span class=\"name\">Do</span>.<span class=\"name\">Internal</span>.<span class=\"name\">VCGen</span>.<span class=\"name\">SolveResult</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult","kind":"inductive","line":30,"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.SolveResult","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/Elab/Tactic/Do/Internal/VCGen/Solve.lean#L30-L45"}}],"imports":["Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Context","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Entails","Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.RuleCache","Lean.Meta.Sym.InstantiateS"],"instances":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.Tactic.Do.Internal.VCGen.Solve"}